name: ohmybank
description: Little bank project for my friends.  At work (yes, we work) we often buy cookies and tea, make gifts at birthday, and so on. Ad-hoc we don't have money for pay, so we remember a debt. But, when we have many events, debt can be lost. At first time, we usee excel. Not bad, but so little automatiozation and human factor: - One pay with creadit card, one with hand-cash - Bankir needs write debts. But also he needs work! Party time in his brain! - Some else
